	(text "Diode prevents capacitors\nfrom powering the shutdown \nloop when the shutdown loop\nopens, without it the capacitors\non the 12V supply of this board \nwould keep the AIRs on for a short\ntime after the loop opens"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 429.641 120.904 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.27 1.27)
			)
			(justify left bottom)
		)
		(uuid "1053d22f-437e-4d7b-961d-c3214e4e1897")
	)
	(text "12V Zener clamps gate voltage of Q3 to 12V,\nand prevents noise or low voltage \naccidentally triggering \"HV Detected\"\nsignal until 12V gate voltage.\n\nStarts conducting at 12V.\nOnce voltage through D14 creates \n1.24V drop across R60, U13 turns on\nlike a low side switch."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 23.368 114.554 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.27 1.27)
			)
			(justify left bottom)
		)
		(uuid "10cdfbf6-7975-496c-9016-d54787066c5c")
	)
	(text "Time constant 1ms rise,\n2ms fall (through pull-down\nresistor). Asymmetry not\nideal, but not a problem\nbecause the signals are\nslow."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 387.223 99.822 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.27 1.27)
			)
			(justify left bottom)
		)
		(uuid "15888b2f-42a0-4744-9073-957cfcbcb088")
	)
	(text "GREEN_LED_ON - true unless TSAC_ACTIVE\nor IMPLAUSIBLE."
